<plot>Quickly marrying successful lawyer Jack Roemer after a whirlwind romance, Haley is certain she's found the man of her dreams. They are both excited to start a family, but when Haley finds out she's pregnant with a girl, Jack is anything but pleased. Haley soon discovers Jack's secret: in order to inherit his family's huge fortune, he must have a son - and he has to do it soon or lose everything. The clock is ticking and Jack will stop at nothing to collect his inheritance - Haley must fight to save her own life and the life of her unborn child.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?117664</url></doc>
